        <IRI>#SymbolFreeSign</IRI>
        <Literal xml:lang="en">DL-query helper: any road sign that explicitly carries zero pictograms/symbols (e.g. the plain priority-road diamond, give-way triangle, no-entry bar). Use this in DL queries instead of the open-world-broken &quot;RoadSign and not (hasSymbol some SymbolRoadSign)&quot; pattern.</Literal>
    </AnnotationAssertion>
